Support Booking.com BV’s strategy for key partners;
Promote the Booking.com BV brand name and its online products and services to key partners;
Create in-depth key accounts profiles that show understanding of the complexity of the Account;
Be the relationship builder for various internal and external stakeholders that are involved in the specific key accounts;
Train, consult, monitor, support internal and external stakeholders in handling the key accounts in order to optimize their performance;
Securing our relationship and optimizing our partnership on a decision making level with key accounts of Booking.com B.V;
Initiate initiatives and present Booking.com B.V. innovations with key accounts to increase performance;
