Monitor internal projects by being the main contact person between Booking.com BV and the key account;
First contact for support to all offices worldwide;
Prepare workshops/trainings;
Run monthly reports on KPI data;
Assist with acquisition preparation;
Assist in preparing internal and external business reviews;
Update administration, wiki, presentations, best practice & acquisition material;
Liaise with XML team and operations for hotels;
Assist in finding solutions for escalated issues.
