Experience in payroll for the US, Multi State, Multi Companies;
Sufficient knowledge of ADP Payroll, Time & Labor Systems, Workday HR
Experience managing internal and external stakeholders;
Excellent communications and customer service skills;
Ability to work effectively as an individual and as a team member;
Ability to manage high volume, fast pace environment;
Ability to take ownership of payroll processes;
